# Force LF for ES-module scripts regardless of core.autocrlf.
# vitest/vite-node mishandles a shebang line that ends in CRLF, so a Windows
# checkout (autocrlf=true) broke collection of e2e/scripts/*.test.mjs (#277).
# All tracked .mjs files were already LF in the index; this pins the working
# tree to match. Node, editors, and CI are all LF-safe.
*.mjs text eol=lf
